author: cbs8
title: Clarification: Apple's News Service-Things To Know story
text: NEW YORK (AP) - In a story Sept. 2, The Associated Press reported that news from the AP will be available on Apple's News app through an RSS feed. Although that was the case in a preliminary, "beta," version of the app, this AP feed isn't expected to be included in the app's broader release.
